OL,3,C'Teachers are clueless': ITV News
OL,4,Creveals new figures for knife crime in
OL,5,Cschools
OL,7,FITV News reveals new figures for knife
OL,8,Fcrime in schools, as North of England
OL,9,FCorrespondent Rachel Townsend reports.
OL,10,FProduced by Senior North of England
OL,11,FProducer Eleanor Gregory
OL,13,FWhy do children carry knives? Power.
OL,14,FProtection. Because "fists don't keep
OL,15,Fus safe".
OL,17,FThese are all responses from children
OL,18,Fwho admitted to ITV News, anonymously,
OL,19,Fthat they have taken a knife into
OL,20,Fschool.
