OL,7,F"I haven't used it - but I've scared
OL,8,Fsome people with it," one of the
OL,9,Fteenagers said.
OL,11,FThey laugh when I ask about getting
OL,12,Fcaught.
OL,14,F"Teachers are clueless," one boy said.
OL,15,F"Clueless. Guys have been searched
OL,16,Fwith stuff on them and still haven't
OL,17,Fgot caught."
OL,19,FIs it pretty easy to hide knives in
OL,20,Fschool?
