OL,7,F"It's easy to hide knives everywhere,"
OL,8,FI am told. "I could name five people
OL,9,Fwho have stabbed people and have got
OL,10,Faway with it. A lot of the stuff is
OL,11,Feasy."
OL,13,FITV News has gained exclusive access
OL,14,Fto figures from police forces across
OL,15,FEngland and Wales on knife possession
OL,16,Fin schools, covering the years from
OL,17,F2019 to 2025.
OL,19,FThey include two grim statistics:
