OL,7,FThe numbers come on the day that the
OL,8,F15-year-old killer of Harvey Willgoose
OL,9,Fwas found guilty of his murder.
OL,11,FIn the five months since Harvey's
OL,12,Fdeath, his parents, Caroline and Mark,
OL,13,Fhave worked to improve the lives of
OL,14,Fyoungsters in their community, in the
OL,15,Fhope it will deter them from carrying
OL,16,Fknives and joining gangs.
