OL,7,F"It's what's keeping us going, we want
OL,8,Fto do some good for our children,
OL,9,Fbecause there are no winners,"
OL,10,FCaroline said, referring to both
OL,11,Fvictims and perpetrators.
OL,13,F"His family, the other person's
OL,14,Ffamily, has got an empty bedroom."
OL,16,FThey want schools to introduce knife
OL,17,Farches, which are walk-through metal
OL,18,Fdetectors that will spot any hidden
OL,19,Fblades.
