OL,7,FAt Archbishop Ilsley Catholic School,
OL,8,Fa comprehensive school in Birmingham,
OL,9,Fthey are doing what they can.
OL,11,FStaff and police carry out spot checks
OL,12,Fon Year 8 pupils, where bags are
OL,13,Fsearched and bodies are scanned.
OL,15,FThey have done this for the last ten
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,18,FWhile no weapons have ever been found,
OL,19,FAssistant Headteacher Dan Corrigan
OL,20,Ftold us they have to be proactive.
